<h3 id="doc-example">Example</h3>
<pre class="html"><code>&lt;div class=&quot;p-0&quot;&gt;No padding&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;px-3 py-2&quot;&gt;Custom horizontal and vertical paddings&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;pt-4 pb-1&quot;&gt;Top and bottom paddings&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;p-2 p-md-5 p-xl-7&quot;&gt;Responsive padding&lt;/div&gt;</code></pre>
<hr />
<h3 id="doc-notes">Notes</h3>
<ul>
<li>All utilities use <code>!important</code> to ensure high
specificity.</li>
<li>These utilities are mobile-first; larger breakpoints override
smaller ones.</li>
</ul>
